orms in the Northeast Atlantic? (1998) B. Am. Meteorol. Soc, 79, pp. 741-760; Woth, K., North Sea storm surge statistics based on projections in a warmer climate: How important are the driving GCM and the chosen emission scenario? (2005) Geophysical Research Letters, 32 (22), pp. 1-4. , DOI 10.1029/2005GL023762, L22708; Woth, K., Weisse, R., Von Storch, H., Climate change and North Sea storm surge extremes: An ensemble study of storm surge extremes expected in a changed climate projected by four different regional climate models (2006) Ocean Dynamics, 56 (1), pp. 3-15. , DOI 10.1007/s10236-005-0024-3","Royal Netherlands Meteorological Institute (KNMI), P.O. Box 201, 3730 AE De Bilt, Netherlands",,,,,,,,18120784,,,,"English","Ocean Sci.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-77956454944
